      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable, functional car who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. While the engine and transmission are in working order and the car drives well, it does show its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents on the exterior, and some visible wear on the interior upholstery. It has been a dependable vehicle, but with higher mileage, it will likely require more frequent routine maintenance than a newer model. It's a solid choice for a daily commuter or a first car for someone on a budget.",
