      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through individual throttle bodies with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with precise shift gates. The chassis has been inspected with the rear subframe reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the M-Variable differential provides exceptional mechanical grip out of corners. Suspension geometry remains true, utilizing factory-spec dampers for a balanced compression and rebound profile. Recent VANOS service ensures optimal valve timing and linear power delivery. This is a driver-focused example with a clean underside and honest mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
